foia:Exemption3StatuteSection.foia:FootnoteText: *In all instances of this exemption other than the single use of 41 U.S.C. §253b(m)(1), we applied it on behalf of another agency, at the other agency’s request.

foia:ProcessedRequestSection.foia:FootnoteText: The pending number at the end of FY 15 does not match the pending number at the beginning of FY 16 for two reasons. FIS reported 95 pending requests at the end of FY 15 when there were only 4. Also, approximately 957 requests relative to OPM’s PII breach were logged in and processed in FY 16, but they were actually received during FY 15. So, the number of pending requests at the start of FY 16 was adjusted to include those requests.
